<codeline><highlight class="normal">##<sp/>🖼️<sp/>Features</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">-<sp/>✅<sp/>OpenGL-powered<sp/>2D<sp/>scene<sp/>rendered<sp/>on<sp/>`wxGLCanvas`</highlight></codeline>
